# KSV-0041: ClusterRole with secrets access
#
# Both the depot-controller and version-controller ClusterRoles include
# secrets: [get] for GetGithubApplicationSecret, which performs a single
# named-object lookup (k8sClient.Get) within the controller's own namespace.
# KSV-0041 fires on any secrets access in a ClusterRole regardless of verb scope.
#
# Production deployments SHOULD use rbac.scopeToNamespace=true, which renders
# these as namespaced Role objects (not ClusterRole) and eliminates this finding.
# The ClusterRole path is only used in the default single-namespace install.
#
# See chart/opendepot/values.yaml rbac.scopeToNamespace for guidance.
KSV-0041

